title: 12/28/2020 - HOUR 2 - Where Colin Was Right, Where Colin Was Wrong & Trent Dilfer
itunes:title: 12/28/2020 - HOUR 2 - Where Colin Was Right, Where Colin Was Wrong & Trent Dilfer
description:
Colin dives in on where he was right and where he was wrong after another week in the NFL and the start of the NBA season. He also talks to Super Bowl champion Trent Dilfer about the Packers win over the Titans and Lamar Jackson’s red hot December.
